hands_on_practices.solution:
我们寻求 $+$ 特征线首次相交的点。沿着从 $x_{0}$ 发出的 $+$ 特征线，我们有
$$J_{+}(x_0)=u+2c,\quad J_{-}=-2c_{0},$$
因此
$$u(x_0)=\frac{J_{+}+J_{-}}{2}
=\frac{2c_{0}+\alpha e^{-x_{0}^{2}/L^{2}}-2c_{0}}{2}
=\frac{\alpha}{2}e^{-x_{0}^{2}/L^{2}},$$
$$c(x_0)=\frac{J_{+}-J_{-}}{4}
=\frac{2c_{0}+\alpha e^{-x_{0}^{2}/L^{2}}+2c_{0}}{4}
=c_{0}+\frac{\alpha}{4}e^{-x_{0}^{2}/L^{2}}.$$
因此特征速度为
$$\lambda_{+}(x_{0})
=u+c
=c_{0}+\frac{3\alpha}{4}e^{-x_{0}^{2}/L^{2}},$$
且射线满足
$$x(t;x_{0})
=x_{0}+c_{0}t+\frac{3\alpha}{4}e^{-x_{0}^{2}/L^{2}}\,t.$$
当以下条件满足时，激波形成
$$\frac{\partial x}{\partial x_{0}}
=1-\frac{3\alpha}{2}\frac{x_{0}t}{L^{2}}e^{-x_{0}^{2}/L^{2}}
=0
\;\Longrightarrow\;
t=\frac{2L^{2}}{3\alpha x_{0}}e^{x_{0}^{2}/L^{2}}.$$
对 $t(x_{0})$ 求最小值可得
$$\frac{dt}{dx_{0}}=0
\;\Longrightarrow\;
x_{0}=\frac{L}{\sqrt2},$$
因此
$$t_{\rm shock}
=\frac{2L^{2}}{3\alpha (L/\sqrt2)}e^{1/2}
=\frac{2\sqrt2\,L}{3\alpha}e^{1/2}.$$
最后

$$
x_{\rm shock}
=x_{0}+c_{0}t_{\rm shock}+\frac{3\alpha}{4}e^{-1/2}t_{\rm shock}
=\frac{L}{\sqrt2}+c_{0}\frac{2\sqrt2\,L}{3\alpha}e^{1/2}
+\frac{\sqrt2\,L}{2}
=\sqrt2\,L\left(1+\frac{2c_{0}e^{1/2}}{3\alpha}\right).
$$
